org.gicentre.geomap

Class AttributeTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gicentre.geomap.AttributeTable
  • Deprecated. 
    Should use Processing's Table class instead. This class is maintained for backward compatibility only (it was written before the Processing Table class).

    @Deprecated
public class AttributeTable
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for representing a table of attributes suitable for querying.
    Version:
    1.3, 4th March, 2017.
    Author:
    Ben Fry (http://ben.fry.com/writing/map/Table.pde) with modifications by Jo Wood and Iain Dillingham, giCentre, City University of London.
